org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.util

类 FoldedTreeSet<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.util.FoldedTreeSet<E>
  • 类型参数:
    E - Entry type
    所有已实现的接口:
    Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Set<E>, SortedSet<E>

    public class FoldedTreeSet<E>
extends Object
implements SortedSet<E>
    A memory efficient implementation of RBTree. Instead of having a Node for each entry each node contains an array holding 64 entries. Based on the Apache Harmony folded TreeMap.

      • addSortedLast

        public boolean addSortedLast(E entry)
        Insert an entry last in the sorted tree. The entry must be the considered larger than the currently largest entry in the set when doing current.compareTo(entry), if entry is not the largest entry the method will fall back on the regular add method.
        参数:
        entry - entry to add
        返回:
        True if added, false if already existed in the set

      • fillRatio

        public double fillRatio()
        Returns the current size divided by the capacity of the tree. A value between 0.0 and 1.0, where 1.0 means that every allocated node in the tree is completely full. An empty set will return 1.0
        返回:
        the fill ratio of the tree

      • compact

        public boolean compact(long timeout)
        Compact all the entries to use the fewest number of nodes in the tree. Having a compact tree minimize memory usage, but can cause inserts to get slower due to new nodes needs to be allocated as there is no space in any of the existing nodes anymore for entries added in the middle of the set. Useful to do to reduce memory consumption and if the tree is know to not change after compaction or mainly added to at either extreme.
        参数:
        timeout - Maximum time to spend compacting the tree set in milliseconds.
        返回:
        true if compaction completed, false if aborted
